							</svg>
						</a>
					</li>
					<li>
						<a href="https://www.youtube.com/anselmobattisti" target="_blank" rel="noopener" aria-label="YouTube" title="YouTube">
							<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" width="24" height="24" fill="currentColor">
								<path d="M23.5 6.2a3.02 3.02 0 0 0-2.13-2.13C19.35 3.5 12 3.5 12 3.5s-7.35 0-9.37.57A3.02 3.02 0 0 0 .5 6.2C0 8.22 0 12 0 12s0 3.78.5 5.8a3.02 3.02 0 0 0 2.13 2.13C4.65 20.5 12 20.5 12 20.5s7.35 0 9.37-.57a3.02 3.02 0 0 0 2.13-2.13C24 15.78 24 12 24 12s0-3.78-.5-5.8ZM9.75 15.5v-7l6 3.5-6 3.5Z"/>
